<h1>Stamford Child Care Permitting Guide 2025</h1>
<p><b>Child Day Care Pre-Application Meeting</b></p>
<p>Applicants can request an inter-departmental pre-application meeting to understand the codes and regulations for opening a Child Daycare. Relevant City departments include the Fire Marshal, Building Department, Transportation Bureau, Health Department, WPCA, and Land Use Bureau. The EPB and Engineering Bureau review the preliminary plans at the pre-application meetings.&nbsp;</p>
